{"tid":2213860,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【中囯又贏】美國眾議院 406-4大比數通過禁用新疆集中營產品","createTime":"2020-09-23T00:29:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T11:06:37.000Z","uid":138409,"like":65,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"2b1dc1baebc50e9aaad209675f2a8846467b2573","tid":2213860,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T00:29:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/adrianzenz/status/1308491794414538752\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fadrianzenz%2Fstatus%2F1308491794414538752&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2%2FZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=659c6989\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fadrianzenz%2Fstatus%2F1308491794414538752&h=e3c972e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/adrianzenz/status/1308491794414538752</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.axios.com/xinjiang-uighur-forced-labor-house-bill-a96b0304-a4c6-4305-97a5-8679b7936987.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axios.com%2Fxinjiang-uighur-forced-labor-house-bill-a96b0304-a4c6-4305-97a5-8679b7936987.html&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2%2FZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=6bc548a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.axios.com/xinjiang-uighur-forced-labor-house-bill-a96b0304-a4c6-4305-97a5-8679b7936987.html</a><br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\">重點</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">提案人</span><br />\n大家都好熟悉嘅<br />\nRep. Jim McGovern (D-Mass.) <br />\n<br />\n參議院法案就係 Marco Rubio (R-Fl.)<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">內容</span>：<br />\n由強迫勞動生產嘅產品，一早已經響美國係犯法<br />\n- 目前嘅法案如果落實，將會令商家有更大責任用「清楚而且具說服力」嘅證據證明自己嘅產品唔係 新疆強迫勞動力 出產<br />\n- 法案通過後90日內，國務卿要決定新疆當地嘅強迫勞動情況係咪「廣泛、系統性並構成罪行（atrocities）」<br />\n- 對於知情地參與新疆強迫勞動嘅人士，總統要辨認並加以簽證或財政制裁<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">相關資料</span>：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rubio.senate.gov/public/index.cfm/2020/3/rubio-mcgovern-lead-bipartisan-bicameral-group-introducing-uyghur-forced-labor-prevention-act?source=email\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rubio.senate.gov%2Fpublic%2Findex.cfm%2F2020%2F3%2Frubio-mcgovern-lead-bipartisan-bicameral-group-introducing-uyghur-forced-labor-prevention-act%3Fsource%3Demail&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2%2FZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=b5999b3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rubio.senate.gov/public/index.cfm/2020/3/rubio-mcgovern-lead-bipartisan-bicameral-group-introducing-uyghur-forced-labor-prevention-act?source=email</a>"},{"pid":"f748a8c4222b15cb6fc3b83f5aa3000e194db81f","tid":2213860,"uid":52658,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T00:30:05.000Z","msg":"邊4票反對<br />\n民主黨定共和黨"},{"pid":"08ebd028cff6d44ea6f143e58f2de837d51117b8","tid":2213860,"uid":138409,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T00:36:19.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"gold\">延伸閱讀</span>：<br />\n<br />\n來自德法意美目前至少五個組織話唔會幫啲商家響新疆嘅供應鏈 提供 勞動審計（labor audit）或 稽查服務，因為成日畀中國當局恐嚇，又要成日用埋啲垃圾官方翻譯員，而且班工人本身都唔夠膽如實反映工作情況。<br />\n此舉將令到商人同新疆供應商嘅合作更困難<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/auditors-say-they-no-longer-will-inspect-labor-conditions-at-xinjiang-factories-11600697706\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fauditors-say-they-no-longer-will-inspect-labor-conditions-at-xinjiang-factories-11600697706&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2%2FZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=12ed8002\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsj.com/articles/auditors-say-they-no-longer-will-inspect-labor-conditions-at-xinjiang-factories-11600697706</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/JChengWSJ/status/1308217198306095105\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJChengWSJ%2Fstatus%2F1308217198306095105&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2%2FZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=06009ed7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJChengWSJ%2Fstatus%2F1308217198306095105&h=d781ca98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/JChengWSJ/status/1308217198306095105</a>"},{"pid":"0fe6d5c95bd0f8e1265843592f3fd5ea783abcfc","tid":2213860,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T00:36:52.000Z","msg":"係咪侵簽完字就過得？"},{"pid":"38a346a339105da113d2033f16c133ac06c6250d","tid":2213860,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f748a8c4222b15cb6fc3b83f5aa3000e194db81f","tid":2213860,"uid":52658,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T00:30:05.000Z","msg":"邊4票反對<br />\n民主黨定共和黨"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T00:37:22.000Z","msg":"未update<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.congress.gov/bill/116th-congress/house-bill/6210\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congress.gov%2Fbill%2F116th-congress%2Fhouse-bill%2F6210&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2%2FZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=8bc1847e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.congress.gov/bill/116th-congress/house-bill/6210</a>"},{"pid":"a1544863fc8f894efa8455434c25482b3ab20762","tid":2213860,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fe6d5c95bd0f8e1265843592f3fd5ea783abcfc","tid":2213860,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T00:36:52.000Z","msg":"係咪侵簽完字就過得？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T00:37:37.000Z","msg":"未過senate"},{"pid":"ba7ed1272c5cf49b25e8881bd7b3d3f0e4a1799f","tid":2213860,"uid":138409,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"38a346a339105da113d2033f16c133ac06c6250d","tid":2213860,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f748a8c4222b15cb6fc3b83f5aa3000e194db81f","tid":2213860,"uid":52658,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T00:30:05.000Z","msg":"邊4票反對<br />\n民主黨定共和黨"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T00:37:22.000Z","msg":"未update<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.congress.gov/bill/116th-congress/house-bill/6210\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congress.gov%2Fbill%2F116th-congress%2Fh